<directions xmlns:php="http://php.net/xsl">&gt;
<step><![CDATA[Beat sugar, hazelnuts in a mortar]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Beat eggs, egg yolks, sugar in a bain-marie, then remove and carry on beating for an extra 5 mins]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Melt butter, dark chocolate in a bain-marie]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Mix the vanilla essence, plain flour, starch, hazelnuts, the beaten eggs, and then the melted chocolate]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Grease a round tin and dust it with flower, then pour the cake mix and bake at 180Â° for 50 mins. Let cool and cut in two slices]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Mix Cognac, Maraschino and sprinkle over each of the two cake halves]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Melt the chocolate over a bain-marie with the cream and beat it. Off the heat add dark chocolate, whipping cream, honey.]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Spread the filling over the top of one of the two halves and place the other on top.]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Melt the apricot jelly, sugar and brush over the cake]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[Melt the chocolate and cover the cake with it]]></step>
&gt;</directions>
